      "writtenOn": "2018-04-20T14:30:51Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Yeah, realistically this just exits and orphans the child, which does half of what daemon() does, but not all of it.\n\nI\u0027d say:\n\n\"Exit immediately after \\fBfork\\fR(2). minijail0 will not act as \\fBinit\\fR(1).\"",
      "parentUuid": "5e3616b0_aa04fc9f",
      "revId": "788e78750ffd500703bf9d12515ed1cf13e5fb14",
      "serverId": "85c56323-6fa9-3386-8a01-6480fb634889",
      "unresolved": true
